  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nWhen you type a decimal '.' in the input field of the gateway, the whole site crashes.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Go to https://gateway.optimism.io/\r\n2. Click on the input value field\r\n3. type one period character '.'  (no numbers)\r\n4. Observe the whole site crashes\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nThis should be a valid input. For example I was trying to type \".25\" ETH\r\n\r\n**Screenshots**\r\nThe whole site screen goes blank white.\r\n\r\n**System Specs:**\r\n - OS: Mac OS\r\n - Browser: Chrome\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nConsole output\r\n`Error: missing value (argument=\"value\", value=\".\", code=INVALID_ARGUMENT, version=bignumber/5.3.0)\r\n    at e.value (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at e.value (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at e.value (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at b (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at Module.$ (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at Nt (main.23afd9bb.chunk.js:1)\r\n    at Pt (main.23afd9bb.chunk.js:1)\r\n    at ra (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at Fa (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at zs (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at ku (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at _u (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at wu (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at du (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at 3.c198524d.chunk.js:2\r\n    at t.unstable_runWithPriority (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at zi (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at Ji (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at Vi (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at 3.c198524d.chunk.js:2\r\n    at Ne (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at De (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at 3.c198524d.chunk.js:2\r\n    at Cn (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at Yt (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at $t (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at t.unstable_runWithPriority (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at zi (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at Re (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at Zt (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)\r\n    at HTMLDivElement.o (3.c198524d.chunk.js:2)`",
